title: Checks any amount of mysql status vars
agents: linux
author: Kuhn & Rue√ü GmbH <info@bkuhn-ruess.de>
license: GPL
distribution: none
description:
 This checks works as subcheck for the Checkmk MySQL plugin.
 This plugin has to be configured in order for this check to work
 If you don't need all of the reported values, just set the disabled services.

 Configuration is via WATO

item:
 The name of each mysql status value as shown in the mysql SHOW STATUS; query

inventory:
 Automatic inventory is supported.
